[{"date":"1953-04-25","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/e3/1a/634633_g8Ua1.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/e3/1a/634633_g8Ua1.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/e3/1a/634633_g8Ua1.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/e3/1a/634633_g8Ua1.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/e3/1a/634633_g8Ua1.jpg"},"summary":"　　阳光明媚，风和日丽的一天。整洁的小院内，大狗史派克正在向他最心疼的儿子传授狗狗的求生技巧，比如将骨头埋在地下，又比如吓唬小猫。与此同时，老猫汤姆正和小老鼠杰瑞在院子里展开了连番的追逐战，他们的打斗自然影响了史派克的说教。史派克将计就计，决定为儿子现身说法，表演如何吓唬猫儿。他信心满满地走到汤姆的背后，突然大声地咆哮起来，吓得汤姆以极快的速度窜上了大树。小狗看的欢喜，跃跃欲试。为了照顾儿子的情绪，史派克将汤姆叫到一边，警告他配合儿子的表演。迫于史派克的强权，汤姆违心同意了。而听到这一切的杰瑞，自然不会放过整治汤姆的大好机会……","name":"That's My Pup!","name_cn":"小犬显威","tags":[{"name":"1950s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猫和老鼠","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"短片","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"小犬显威"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1953年4月25日"},{"key":"片长","value":"7分钟"},{"key":"IMDb","value":"tt0046417"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":5,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":2,"7":2,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":0,"wish":0,"collect":6,"doing":0},"id":634633,"eps":0,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1953-04-18","platform":"其他","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/04/64/241617_157Q2.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/04/64/241617_157Q2.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/04/64/241617_157Q2.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/04/64/241617_157Q2.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/04/64/241617_157Q2.jpg"},"summary":"　　Mickey and Pluto take a trip to the beach, and as the formula goes, the dog gets into mishaps that he is unable to explain to Mickey. In this instance, it's a testy clam. Then Mickey goes fishing, but seagulls eat all the bait, and just generally spoil 